   Francisco: W.H. Freeman.
<dt>Retallack, G.J. 1992. "Paleosols and changes in climate and vegetation across 
   the Eocene/ Oligocene boundary," in <em>Eocene-Oligocene Climactic and Biotic 
   Evolution</em>, D.R. Prothero and W.A. Berggren (eds.). Princeton: Princeton 
   University Press. pp. 382-398.
