<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>About Frank Miele</TITLE>
<LINK REV = "made" HREF = "mailto:lippard@skeptic.com">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
Frank Miele began writing for <EM>Skeptic</EM> with an essay on the
free-speech aspects of Holocaust revisionism (<A HREF = "02.4.miele-holocaust.html">"Giving the Devil His
