<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>About Jim Lippard and Jeff Jacobsen</TITLE>
<LINK REV = "made" HREF = "mailto:lippard@skeptic.com">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
Jim Lippard has an M.A. in Philosophy from the University of Arizona
and was the founder of the Phoenix Skeptics.  He authored "Sun Goes
Down in Flames: The Jammal Ark Hoax," in <EM>Skeptic</EM> Vol. 2, No. 3 and
is <EM>Skeptic</EM>'s contact person on the Internet.
<A HREF = "mailto:lippard@skeptic.com">
He may be reached via email as lippard@skeptic.com.
</A>

<P>Jeff Jacobsen has a B.A. in Religious Studies from Arizona State
University.  He was in a small Christian cult from 1972-1978.  He is
a contact person for the Cult Awareness Network, based in Chicago.
<A HREF = "mailto:cultxpt@primenet.com">
He may be reached on the Internet as cultxpt@primenet.com.
</A>
</BODY>
