<DT>67. For the story of the discovery of HIV see ref. 14 (Shilts); also 
Grmek, M., ref 14. 
<DT>68. Rev Infect Dis 7(1):75-82, 1985. 
<DT>69. J Acquir Immune Defic Syndr 4:547-557, 1991. 
<DT>70. Gastroenterol Jpn 25 Suppl 2:38-42, 1990. 
<DT>71. J Infect Dis 170:543-52, 1994. 
