<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Is There Really A Cosmological Crisis?</TITLE>
<LINK REV = "made" HREF = "mailto:lippard@skeptic.com">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
From <EM>Skeptic</EM> vol. 3, no. 4, 1995, pp. 42-45.
<P>The following article is copyright &#169 1995 by the Skeptics 
Society,
P.O. Box 338, Altadena, CA 91001, (818) 794-3119.  Permission
has been granted for noncommercial electronic circulation of this
article in its entirety, including this notice.
<A HREF = "skeptic-subs.html">  A special Internet introductory 
