Posted by grasshopper on January 05, 1997 at 20:55:37:<p>
In Reply to: <a href="843.html">Re: Full Skeptics??</a> posted by Stephen Charchuk on January 04, 1997 at 23:47:02:<p>
: : The original question was did I believe I think therefore I am...the answer<br>: : is no-I don't believe that I think....I may simply be the voice of god.<p>: What is thinking? As to the second part of your reply, don't be ridiculous. (g)<p>David asked the question if I believe 'I think therefore I am', but I <br>don't actually know how he is defining 'thinking'...I assume he<br>meant a being of independent mind-but I don't know exactly what was meant.<br>For the purpose of my aurguement I was using thinking to mean just<br>that I do in fact make desions independently (to some extent of course)<br>rather than simply be robot.  
