Comments:<br>
<textarea name="body" COLS=70 ROWS=20>
: : : I think because I don't believe one way or another about anything my
: : : mind is completely open to all things...Hopefully my brain won't fall
: : : out...
: : Total non-belief is a sign of a closed mind, a skeptic is willing to
: : listen and accept if the evidence is sound.

: I am certainly open to evidence...As far as I know I can not know and 
: therefore believe (or not believe) in anything...I certainly would
: welcome any proof of anything.  I am totally open to new ideas/theories
: because I have no believes of my own to close my mind.

</textarea>
