: Interesting idea but I see one area where it might make things a bit fuzzy - 
: Homosexuality is considered immoral by many (destructive in this case-or evil) but moral to others (constructive-good), yesterday the same thing occured with the equality of women, the day before it was slavery. How could you weigh these issues? 

