: : Hello Again,
: : You're not rude at all.  I'm enjoying our conversation.  I suppose I'm trying desperately to present a reasonable explanation for my faith.  Maybe it's just not possible to explain supernatural things in a natural way.

: Head on the nail. That's why we call it supernatural isn't it? That's also why we can't be rational and have faith in god at the same time.
: : God just can't be understood in scientific terms, anymore than one could prove or explain a passionate love for another person.  Science could logically say that love is merely a nuerological response to certain stimuli, yet for anyone who has ever experienced true love, it is much, much more.

