: I'm afraid I've offended you.  I declared that I was not proslytizing, and then I did.  Forgive me.
: I visited your web site and I'm quite impressed.  It's a trip that a housewife in Michigan can have stimulating conversation with a highly educated student in Sweden.  
: I wonder now if I haven't misunderstood your point.  I certainly don't think you would have to throw away everything you have learned and come to believe in order to be acceptable to God.  Why would He expect us NOT to explore the workings of nature and the universe.
: Personally, I find no disagreement between scientific discovery and what the Bible says.  But enough of that, let's move to some other debate.  

