Posted by Jason on January 04, 1997 at 00:02:58:<p>
In Reply to: <a href="754.html">Re: Logic</a> posted by Grasshopper on January 02, 1997 at 14:28:19:<p>
: : Sorry, but you sound like an angry teenager.<p>: Seeing that I'm new to the page I would suggest you figure out what<br>: I really think before you post offensive remarks.<p>Mr. Grasshopper, I just realized something. Given your philosophy, you are<br>being inconsistent by complaining about Lynn's comments. How do you define<br>the word "offensive?" Obviously, by inductive reasoning. But wait, you don't<br>believe in anything. How could you know what an offensive remark is? To believe<br>that a remark is offensive, you have to believe in certain things first.<p>By responding to Lynn this way you're revealing some basic assumptions and<br>this is inconsistent with your epistemology.<br>- Jason<br>
