<br>: You believe others are decieved by lying spirits, but not you...obviously??!!!<br>: Actually I don't believe in history-any kind religious or otherwise.  I don't<br>: believe those people actually excisted, and I don't know that people are truthful, or <br>: a million (millions and millions) of other quite possible theories.<br>: I'm the ultimate skeptic-I don't believe (or totally disbelieve)in ANYTHING.<br>: respectfully, grasshopper<p><p>What grade are you in?
