    <center>
      <h1>Tai Chi</h1>
    </center>
<hr size=7 width=75%>
<center>[ <a href="#followups">Follow Ups</a> ] [ <a href="#postfp">Post Followup</a> ] [ <a href="http://www.skeptic.com/skepticboard/skepticboard.html">Skeptics Society Message Board</a> ] [ <a href="http://www.skeptic.com/skepticboard/faq.html">FAQ</a> ]</center>
<hr size=7 width=75%><p>
Posted by Jason on January 04, 1997 at 00:49:52:<p>
Does anyone know much about Tai Chi? I've heard some claims that<br>Tai Chi masters have paranormal abilities. For example, one claim<br>is that a Tai Chi master can immobilize an attacker simply by pointing<br>at him. Naturally, I'm skeptical of these claims.<p>I guess if Tai Chi masters did have extraordinary abilities, it may<br>not necessarily be a supernatural or spiritual phenomenon. It may be<br>some physical effect that we have yet to understand scientifically.<br>- Jason
<br>
